{"_path":"/2025/05/shr-misskey","_dir":"05","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"我又用了一段时间 Misskey，发现和 Sharkey 存在一些区别和不足","description":"本文介绍了个人在重新使用一段时间 Misskey 后，得出与 Sharkey 相比存在一些区别和不足。","date":"2025-05-22T03:30:00.000Z","categories":["联邦宇宙"],"tags":["Fediverse","Misskey","Sharkey"],"image":"https://blog-files.101045700.xyz/Fediverse/MisskeyHome.png","readingTime":{"text":"7 min read","minutes":6.16,"time":369600,"words":1232},"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"前言"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"前言"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"最近在 Fediverse 的其他实例（咪社）开了一个自己的“分身”："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"账号信息：@"},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"mailto:NukiMiku@misskey.site"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"NukiMiku@misskey.site"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"先不解释开这个分身的目的是什么，之前在个人实例一直是使用 Sharkey 作为个人使用程序，借着开分身我也算是重新体验了原汁原味的 Misskey。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"不过在使用之后，却发现与 Sharkey 相比存在了一些区别和不足（可能自己被 Sharkey 惯坏了）。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"不足"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"不足"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"我所说的任何不足都没有批判 Misskey 的意思，毕竟 Sharkey 是它的分支版本，做出自己的任何更改 Misskey 都没有义务去遵守合并。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"缺失直接编辑"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"缺失直接编辑"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"我在发帖的时候有时可能比较着急和欠考虑，发出去之后就可能想改一下。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"于是我打开 Misskey 的帖子额外菜单寻思再“编辑”一下。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"然后我发现只有“删除并编辑”，之前在使用 Sharkey 时是有直接编辑这个选项的。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"没有直接编辑功能分别是存在好处和坏处的："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"好处："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"与其他程序（Gotosocial，Mastodon）的兼容效果会更好，这些程序也没有直接意义上的“编辑”选项。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"del","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"不会有别人知道你曾经写错了帖子。"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"坏处："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"对于一些发布时间较久的帖子，你如果发现错误想要修改，你再选择“删除并编辑”就有点突兀了。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"总之在这点上个人还是站 Sharkey 这边的，尤其是最近发现自己比较久远帖子有个错误时候（也没有不承认错误“毁尸灭迹”的意思，实际上 Sharkey 会展示这个帖子的历史编辑，当然也可能会略占用更多数据库资源）。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"缺失单独私密化"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"缺失单独“私密化”（"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"如果说上面没有直接编辑还能找理由的话， Misskey 有关这个帖子没有单独的“私密化”设置我就有点想不通了。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"alert","props":{"type":"question"},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"template","props":{"v-slot:title":""},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"什么是“私密化”？"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"似乎是在 Misskey 系列中出现的功能，用户可以把“私密化”标签打到帖子上，然后这个帖子就会进入“私密”状态，只有用户自己才能看到这个帖子的内容。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"不过实际上可能只有 Misskey 系列程序会遵守“私密化”，聊胜于无吧。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在 Misskey 里只能为某个时间段之前的帖子做出“私密化”，也就是“一私私一片”。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"而在 Sharkey 里，我们就可以单独为帖子“私密化”，而不是群体私密化。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"这点 Misskey 还是不大舒服的其实。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"缺失注册审批"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"缺失注册审批"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"这点我其实现在也不是很清楚 Misskey 是否已经完善了，总之 Sharkey 还是有的，当多管理员或者审批组时会很有用，即“开放注册”但需要“填写注册理由”然后等待“管理审核”，这样相对来说比直接使用邀请码注册开放，也更安全。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"差异"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"差异"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"差异包含了一些“不那么重要”或者说“低使用率”的需求。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"listenbrainz-集成"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"ListenBrainz 集成"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"个人不是十分了解这个集成方式，同实例的朋友之前有使用过："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"贴文："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://circle.tkg3.top/notes/a60lb602rznr000m","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"https://circle.tkg3.top/notes/a60lb602rznr000m"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"兼容-mastodon-api"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"兼容 Mastodon API"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Sharkey 在他们文档里有表示他们兼容 Mastodon 的 API，直观点理解就是可以使用 Mastodon 的客户端程序登陆和管理你的 Sharkey。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"这点个人其实用不大上，为了去验证也拿 Mastodon 的客户端试了下，确实可以登录并且发帖等。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"当然其实还是用处不大，毕竟 Misskey 的特色功能全都无法正常使用，MfM 语法也无法正常显示，插入表情可能也会出现差异问题。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"像猫一样说话与是猫分开"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"“像猫一样说话”与“是猫”分开"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"其实就是可以设定获得猫耳但不学猫说话（）"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"但是 Misskey 确实只能同时获得。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"ui-风格变化"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"UI 风格变化"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","v